 Meebit from your declared wallet, and then you take the $50 million of=C2=
=A0cryptocurrency out of the declared wallet and put it back in your (legit=
imate) bank account, and then you write the IRS a check for $20 million say=
ing =E2=80=9Cah I=E2=80=99ve been selling NFTs, what fun I have had, but I =
have to pay the IRS my fair share,=E2=80=9D then =E2=80=A6=C2=A0I am obviou=
sly not going to give you advice on crime but it=E2=80=99s possible you=E2=
=80=99ve got something there?=C2=A0Like, nobody has any idea what a Meebit =
is worth, so this string of outlandish numbers is somewhat plausible? It=E2=
